  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Trade and Development/UN Global Compact</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The United Nations Global Compact Trust Fund supports the work of the Global Compact Office and global activities. UNGC advances the implementation of Finland&apos;s development policy through thematic Aid for Trade (AFT). The private sector&apos;s commitment to Cor
porate Social Responsibility in the framework of the ten UNGC principles on human rights, labour, the environment and anti-corruption integrates the cross-cutting themes into Finland&apos;s AFT. UNGC improves the role of the UN System in Finland&apos;s multilateral 
AFT. UNGC can also, for its own part, reduce risks related to partnerships between the state and businesses in development cooperation.</narrative>
  </description>
